\c 9
\s Inhlupheko yesihlanu: Isifo sezifuyo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yana kuFaro\x + 8.1,2.\x* uthi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru\x + 7.16.\x*, \add ithi\add*: Yekela abantu bami bahambe ukuthi bangikhonze.
\v 2 Ngoba uba usala ukubayekela bahambe, ulokhu ubabambile,
\v 3 khangela, isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* sizakuba phezu kwezifuyo zakho ezisegangeni, phezu kwamabhiza, phezu kwabobabhemi, phezu kwamakamela, phezu kwenkomo laphezu kwezimvu, umatshayabhuqe wesifo onzima kakhulu\x + 7.4.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza umehluko phakathi kwezifuyo zakoIsrayeli lezifuyo zeGibhithe\x + 8.22; 11.7.\x*, kuze kuthi kakuyikufa lutho kukho konke okwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimisa isikhathi esimisiweyo, isithi: Kusasa iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwenza linto elizweni.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yayenza-ke linto kusisa; lazo zonke izifuyo zeGibhithe zafa\x + Hlab. 78.50. 9.19.\x*; kodwa kakufanga lesisodwa ezifuyweni zabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 7 UFaro wasethuma, khangela-ke, kakufanga ngitsho lesisodwa ezifuyweni zakoIsrayeli. Kodwa inhliziyo kaFaro yaba nzima\x + 8.15.\x*, kasiyekelanga isizwe sihambe.
\s Inhlupheko yesithupha: Amathumba
\p
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi lakuAroni: Zithatheleni izandla zenu ezigcweleyo zomlotha weziko, njalo uMozisi awutsahazele emazulwini phambi kwamehlo kaFaro.
\v 9 Njalo uzakuba luthuli olucolekileyo phezu kwelizwe lonke leGibhithe, njalo luzakuba phezu kwabantu laphezu kwezifuyo lube lithumba eliphihlika amathuthuva\x + Levi 13.18,19. Dute. 28.27. 2 Kho. 20.7. Jobe 2.7. Isam. 16.2.\x* elizweni lonke leGibhithe.
\v 10 Basebethatha umlotha weziko, bema phambi kukaFaro; uMozisi wasewutsahazela emazulwini, waba lithumba eliphihlika amathuthuva ebantwini lezifuyweni\x + 9.8.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo abalumbi\x + 7.11; 8.18,19. 2 Tim. 3.9.\x* babengeme phambi kukaMozisi ngenxa yamathumba; ngoba amathumba ayephezu kwabalumbi laphezu kwawo wonke amaGibhithe.
\v 12 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yayenza yaba lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro\x + 4.21.\x*, njalo kazabezwa, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi.
\s Inhlupheko yesikhombisa: Isiqhotho
\p
\v 13 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Vuka ekuseni kakhulu, uzimise phambi kukaFaro uthi kuye\x + 7.15; 8.20.\x*: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru \add ithi\add*: Yekela isizwe sami sihambe bangikhonze\x + 7.16.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba ngalesisikhathi ngizathumela zonke inhlupheko zami enhliziyweni yakho laphezu kwenceku zakho laphezu kwesizwe sakho, ukuze wazi ukuthi kakho onjengami emhlabeni wonke\x + 8.10.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba khathesi ngizaselula isandla sami ukuze ngikutshaye lesizwe sakho ngomatshayabhuqe wesifo, ubusuchitheka usuke emhlabeni.
\v 16 Kodwa isibili ngalokhu ngikumisile ukuze ngikutshengise amandla ami lokuze ibizo lami lilandiswe emhlabeni wonke\x + 10.1,2; 11.9; 14.17. Zaga 16.4. Roma 9.17.\x*.
\v 17 Usaziphakamisa umelana labantu bami, ukuthi ungabayekeli bahambe yini?
\v 18 Khangela, kusasa ngalesisikhathi ngizanisa isiqhotho esinzima kakhulu, esingazanga sibe khona esinjalo eGibhithe kusukela ngosuku lisekelwa kuze kube khathesi.
\v 19 Khathesi-ke thuma, ubuthe izifuyo zakho lakho konke olakho ensimini; wonke umuntu layo yonke inyamazana okuficwa ensimini okungabuthelwanga ekhaya, nxa isiqhotho siwela phezu kwakho, kuzakufa.
\v 20 Lowo olesabayo ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* phakathi kwenceku zikaFaro wenza izisebenzi zakhe lezifuyo zakhe zibalekele ezindlini;
\v 21 kodwa lowo ongabekanga inhliziyo yakhe elizwini leN\nd kosi\nd* watshiya izisebenzi zakhe lezifuyo zakhe ensimini.
\p
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yelulela isandla sakho emazulwini, ukuze kube khona isiqhotho\x + Isam. 16.21.\x* elizweni lonke leGibhithe, phezu kwabantu laphezu kwezinyamazana laphezu kwemibhida yonke yensimu elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 23 UMozisi waseselulela intonga yakhe emazulwini; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasiletha imidumo lesiqhotho\x + Hlab. 78.47,48; 105.32. Josh. 10.11. Hlab. 18.13; 148.8. Isa. 30.30. Hez. 38.22. Isam. 8.7.\x*; lomlilo wehlela emhlabeni; leN\nd kosi\nd* yanisa isiqhotho elizweni leGibhithe.
\v 24 Kwasekusiba khona isiqhotho, lomlilo uzixubanise esiqhothweni\x + Hez. 1.4.\x*; okunzima kakhulu; okungazanga kube khona okunjengakho elizweni lonke leGibhithe selokhu laba yisizwe.
\v 25 Isiqhotho sasesitshaya elizweni lonke leGibhithe konke okusegangeni, kusukela ebantwini kusiya ezinyamazaneni; lesiqhotho satshaya wonke umbhida weganga, sephula sonke isihlahla seganga\x + Hlab. 105.33.\x*.
\v 26 Kuphela elizweni leGosheni lapho ababekhona abantwana bakoIsrayeli kwakungekho isiqhotho\x + 8.22; 9.4,6; 10.23; 11.7; 12.13.\x*.
\p
\v 27 UFaro wasethuma wabiza uMozisi loAroni, wathi kubo: Ngonile ngalesisikhathi\x + 10.16.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* ilungile, kanti mina labantu bami sibabi\x + 2 Lan. 12.6. Lilo 1.18.\x*.
\v 28 Ncengani iN\nd kosi\x + 8.8,28; 10.17. Seb. 8.24.\x*\nd*, ngoba sekwanele, ukuze kungabi lemidumo elamandla lesiqhotho; besengiliyekela lihambe, lingabe lisahlala.
\v 29 UMozisi wasesithi kuye: Nxa sengiphumile emzini, ngizachaya izandla zami eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 9.33. 1 Kho. 8.22,38. Hlab. 143.6. Isa. 1.15.\x*; kuzaphela imidumo lesiqhotho kasisayikuba khona, ukuze wazi ukuthi umhlaba ungoweN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 24.1. 1 Kor. 10.26,28.\x*\nd*.
\v 30 Kodwa wena lenceku zakho, ngiyazi ukuthi kalikayesabi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu.
\v 31 Kwasekutshaywa \w ifilakisi\w** \w lebhali\w**; ngoba ibhali yayisesikwetshini, lefilakisi yayisithela amaluba\x + Levi 2.14.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa ingqoloyi \w lespelite\w** kakutshaywanga, ngoba kwakungakavuthwa.
\v 33 UMozisi wasephuma emzini evela kuFaro, wachaya izandla zakhe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 9.29.\x*; kwasekusima imidumo lesiqhotho, lezulu kalabe li\add sa\add*thululeka emhlabeni.
\v 34 Kwathi uFaro esebonile ukuthi izulu lesiqhotho lemidumo sekumile, wengezelela ukona, wayenza yaba nzima inhliziyo yakhe, yena lenceku zakhe\x + 1 Sam. 6.6.\x*.
\v 35 Njalo inhliziyo kaFaro yaba lukhuni\x + 7.13.\x*, kazabayekela abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahambe, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yayitshilo ngesandla sikaMozisi.
